Notes: Personal papers, family papers, and organizational records, books, periodcials, prints and photographs documenting the experiences and contributions of African Americans particularly in the Southeastern United States, emphasizing the areas of education, literature, religion, politics, social work, civil rights, and race relations.  Also there is historical documentation about the Atlanta University Center institutions.  Members:  Clark Atlanta University, Interdenominational Theological Center, Morehouse College, Spelman College
